::Slayer::

Slayer lands in the Trainer base, setting Ignatius down.

"Get repaired if you need to," he says, already walking toward the 
bridge, "I'm gonna get working."

Slayer was damaged, but he could wait. Rescuing Prebon was much more 
important.


--- In nbwrpg@y..., Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Slayer::
> 
> Slayer looks ahead, watching the Trainer base approaching. Once 
> repaired, he would plan someway to get Prebon back. Prebon WOULD 
> return to the Trainers, Slayer was sure of it.
